### Agent Actions for HTML Report

1. Read `test-results/[component-name]-report.json` for data
2. If `test-results/storybook-test-report.html` exists, read it to preserve existing component tabs
3. Build/update HTML with real test results from JSON
4. For new components: add a new component tab and section
5. For re-tested components: replace that component's section with updated data
6. Write to `test-results/storybook-test-report.html`

